FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1774372288
OL,3,CReform candidate urged to apologise
OL,4,Cover 'appalling' social media posts
OL,6,FIn August 2024, she replied: "Me," to
OL,7,Fa post on the social media site X from
OL,8,FAshlea Simon, the deputy leader of the
OL,9,Ffar-right party Britain First, which
OL,10,Fsaid: "In the UK Muslims are demanding
OL,11,Fthat sharia law is implemented. I
OL,12,Fdemand that we deport the lot of them.
OL,13,FWho's with me?"
OL,15,FThe previous month, she sent a message
OL,16,Fsaying: "Behind you all the way," to
OL,17,FRobinson, whose real name is Stephen
OL,18,FYaxley-Lennon, after he posted about
OL,19,F"setting up in Trafalgar Square for
OL,20,Fthe biggest patriotic rally the UK has
OL,21,Fever seen".
OL,26,@nD@^OUnD@bO]rD@GOUuD@OO]xD@IOUxD@aO]{D@
OL,26,AAOU}D@JO]
