OL,3,CReform candidate urged to apologise
OL,4,Cover 'appalling' social media posts
OL,6,FIn the following days she sent a
OL,7,F"thumbs up" emoji to a post that said:
OL,8,F"Give me a Thumbs Up and RETWEET, If
OL,9,FYOU STAND WITH TOMMY ROBINSON" (sic).
OL,11,FShe also replied "Yes" to a post that
OL,12,Fsaid: "Do YOU agree with what Tommy
OL,13,FRobinson says! YES or NO?"
OL,15,FReform UK leader Nigel Farage has
OL,16,Fconsistently said that Robinson is not
OL,17,Fwelcome in the party.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@KO]pD@AOUqD@^O]qD@`pmqD@dpnsD@
OL,26,AROUsD@VO]tD@GOUuD@ZO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
