PN,35504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1774372288
OL,3,CReform candidate urged to apologise
OL,4,Cover 'appalling' social media posts
OL,6,FEarlier that month, Beresford had
OL,7,Freplied "Yes" to a post that read:
OL,8,F"Was Enoch Powell RIGHT? Please
OL,9,FRetweet..... YES or NO?".
OL,11,FITV Border has approached Beresford
OL,12,Fand Reform UK for comment.
OL,14,FA Reform source said they did not
OL,15,Fbelieve Beresford still held those
OL,16,Fviews and said that "everyone is
OL,17,Fentitled to a past".
OL,19,FThey said Beresford has "a lot to
OL,20,Foffer" as a "really down to earth
OL,21,Fbusinesswoman and mum".
OL,26,@oD@IOUoD@MO]pD@AOUqD@XO]xD@UOUyD@SO]{D@
OL,26,AYOU|D@FO]|D@MOU}D@VO]
