CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1774372288
OL,3,CReform candidate urged to apologise
OL,4,Cover 'appalling' social media posts
OL,6,FScottish Labour leader Anas Sarwar
OL,7,Fdescribed the comments as "appalling",
OL,8,Fadding that Beresford is "totally
OL,9,Funfit for public office".
OL,11,FHe added: "It has taken a matter of
OL,12,Fhours for Reform Scotland's big launch
OL,13,Fto fall apart and their true colours
OL,14,Fto show.
OL,16,F"If Nigel Farage refuses to act and
OL,17,Fremove this candidate, Malcolm Offord
OL,18,Fmust step up and show some leadership
OL,19,Fhimself.
OL,26,@sD@KOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1774372288
OL,3,CReform candidate urged to apologise
OL,4,Cover 'appalling' social media posts
OL,6,F"This incident has confirmed once and
OL,7,Ffor all how poisonous and chaotic
OL,8,FReform is and I have no doubt that
OL,9,FScots will send them packing."
OL,11,FConservative Galloway and West
OL,12,FDumfries MSP Finlay Carson said: "She
OL,13,Fhas made her position quite clear. It
OL,14,Fis not a view that I know the majority
OL,15,Fof people in Dumfries and Galloway
OL,16,Fwould support. They would find it
OL,17,Fcompletely out of order. It's not
OL,18,Fbecoming of someone who is seeking a
OL,19,Fpublic position."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@^O]tD@bOU{D@QO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
