OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1774372288
OL,3,CReform candidate urged to apologise
OL,4,Cover 'appalling' social media posts
OL,6,FThe SNP's South Scotland MSP Emma
OL,7,FHarper called the posts "a bit
OL,8,Fworrying," adding: "I think the public
OL,9,Fwill judge what the messages are in
OL,10,Fthe tweets....Frankly they are not
OL,11,Fvery nice for people that we should be
OL,12,Fwelcoming in Scotland."
OL,14,FSpeaking at the launch of Reform's
OL,15,FScottish election manifesto, where its
OL,16,FHolyrood constituency candidates were
OL,17,Falso unveiled, Farage said he was
OL,18,F"very" confident in his party's
OL,19,Fvetting process.
OL,26,@oD@YOUpD@JO]pD@TOUtD@WO]zD@AOUzD@FO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1774372288
OL,3,CReform candidate urged to apologise
OL,4,Cover 'appalling' social media posts
OL,6,F"These candidates have all been put
OL,7,Fthrough their paces, goodness me," he
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,F"They've been sat down, they've been
OL,11,Fgiven hostile interviews as part of
OL,12,Ftheir preparation, we've vetted them
OL,13,Fthoroughly. I'm very, very confident
OL,14,Fof the group we've got."
OL,16,FAsked if there were any candidates he
OL,17,Fwas "expecting difficult questions
OL,18,Fabout", Farage added: "I'm not
OL,19,Fexpecting any especially difficult
OL,20,Fquestions about any of them but we'll
OL,21,Fhave to see, won't we."
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@bO]rD@AOUvD@XO]yD@EOUzD@FO]zD@
OL,26,AWOU}D@WO]
